            "date_published": "2023-08-07T13:54:09.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>  ESP32 是一款流行的 WiFi 和蓝牙片上系统 （SoC）</p>\n<p>  利用 Thonny    和 Micropython 进行编程调试</p>\n<hr>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"点亮led灯\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#点亮led灯\">#</a> 点亮 LED 灯</h4>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> machine<br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> time<br><br>pin2 = machine.Pin(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, machine.Pin.OUT)<br><br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">True</span>:<br>    pin2. value(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)<br>    time. sleep(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)<br>    pin2. value(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)<br>    time. sleep(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"pwm呼吸灯\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#pwm呼吸灯\">#</a> PWM 呼吸灯</h4>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs python\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> machine <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> Pin, PWM<br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> time<br><br>led2 = PWM(Pin(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>))<br>led2 = freq(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span>)<br><br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">True</span>:<br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 控制整体的重复(1.从不亮便慢变亮  2. 从亮慢慢到不亮)</span><br>    <br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 1.从不亮慢慢变亮</span><br>\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1024</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>):<br>\tled2.duty(i)<br>\ttime.sleep_ms(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)<br><br>\t<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 2.从亮慢慢到不亮</span><br>\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1023</span>, -<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, -<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>):<br>\tled2. duty(i)<br>\ttime.sleep_ms(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"连接wifi热点\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#连接wifi热点\">#</a> 连接 WIFI 热点</h4>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n",
